  {
    "id": 160800001001000150,
    "value": "You can never become a real man without getting a few bruises!"
  },
  {
    "id": 160800001001000250,
    "value": "You're right. We'd all be dead if it wasn't for you."
  },
  {
    "id": 160800001001000750,
    "value": "Hehe, you really didn't feel anything?"
  },
  {
    "id": 160800001013000150,
    "value": "I'm gonna be a big shot! I can't crap out now!"
  },
  {
    "id": 160800001031000150,
    "value": "I have to stop loving you. Then, I'll be able to order you to meet your demise."
  },
  {
    "id": 160800001060000150,
    "value": "Stay alert! Lose focus and you'll die in the blink\nof an eye!"
  },
  {
    "id": 160800001060000250,
    "value": "You won't be leaving Cima behind!"
  },
  {
    "id": 160800001080000150,
    "value": "Our only option now is to fight... I have to do my part."
  },
  {
    "id": 160800001080000250,
    "value": "Lieutenant Emma is the flower of the Radish, and this ship will always be there for her."
  },
  {
    "id": 160800001080000550,
    "value": "You just need to wake up.\nThen, you'll be yourself again."
  },
  {
    "id": 160800001095000150,
    "value": "All right! All hands, to your stations! Nahel Argama, launch!"
  },
  {
    "id": 160800001095000350,
    "value": "If you don't stand with me for justice, then get out of my sight!"
  },
  {
    "id": 160800001110000150,
    "value": "This is an independent operation. Forward, Londo Bell!"
  },
  {
    "id": 160800001125000250,
    "value": "I'm counting on you all!"
  },
  {
    "id": 160800001125000450,
    "value": "I shoulder much responsibility\nas heir to the Zabi bloodline!"
  },
  {
    "id": 160800001150000150,
    "value": "Mafty doesn't handle things the right way."
  },
  {
    "id": 160800001200000150,
    "value": "But...we're partners! \nYou have to let me fight with you!"
  },
  {
    "id": 160800001200000350,
    "value": "Bwahahaha!"
  },
  {
    "id": 160800001210000150,
    "value": "Peace can never come out of war."
  },
  {
    "id": 160800001210000350,
    "value": "You don't treat the battle field seriously enough!"
  },
  {
    "id": 160800001230000150,
    "value": "I'll Give You Power..."
  },
  {
    "id": 160800001230000350,
    "value": "Can Newtypes really create a new future?\nI have to see for myself."
  },
  {
    "id": 160800001300000150,
    "value": "Ready the Lohengrin!"
  },
  {
    "id": 160800001300000450,
    "value": "Power or desire alone is not enough..."
  },
  {
    "id": 160800001300000550,
    "value": "Welcome to the ship of the songstress.\nI am Andrew Waltfeld."
  },
  {
    "id": 160800001300000650,
    "value": "Violence isn't the answer, you know."
  },
  {
    "id": 160800001305000250,
    "value": "Communications, maintenance, I can do it all!"
  },
  {
    "id": 160800001305000350,
    "value": "-"
  },
  {
    "id": 160800001330000250,
    "value": "Tannhäuser online! Targeting enemy ahead!\nFire!"
  },
  {
    "id": 160800001370000150,
    "value": "This is the big debut for Celestial Being."
  },
  {
    "id": 160800001370000450,
    "value": "Conflict doesn't create anything.\nIt only destroys!"
  },
  {
    "id": 160800001400000150,
    "value": "The specter of revenge haunts me!"
  },
  {
    "id": 160800001430000150,
    "value": "We'll get there...together!"
  },
  {
    "id": 160800001430000350,
    "value": "I must live up to my responsibilities, for those who believe in me."
  },
  {
    "id": 160800001430000450,
    "value": "Gjallarhorn exists to maintain order in the world."
  },
  {
    "id": 160800001430000550,
    "value": "I-I need to do my part!"
  },
  {
    "id": 160800001501000150,
    "value": "I refuse to lose what is dearest to my heart."
  },
  {
    "id": 160800001705000150,
    "value": "Power is countered by magic, and magic by power. That's the basic rule of battle."
  }
]